title: Macromedia Dreamweaver 8 Pro (+Serial)
description:
Macromedia Dreamweaver 8 Pro
--------------------------

Product Features

 - Visual authoring with XML data and a new, unified CSS panel 

 - Style-rendering toolbar and CSS rendering tools 

 - Improved WebDAV supports digest authentication and SSL, for better server connectivity and secure file transfer 

 - Compare page layouts to comps with pixel-perfect accuracy, using guides to measure page layouts 

 - New zoom features - Pan in and inspect images or work with complex nested table layouts  

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

System Requirements

Platform:    Windows 98 / 2000 / XP, Mac OS X
